View contents of gRPC web network requests.

No setup, no code changes needed. Works in development and production environments. Familiar experience similar to native network devtools. Works with HAR files recorded elsewhere.

Note that decoding from binary format is not perfect as it doesn't include field names or types. Output is similar to protoscope syntax (see examples in screenshots).
